title: Catalonia Votes on Independence
subtitle: The non-binding consultation calls millions to the polls
face-image: img/events/9n.jpg
new-page: true
tags: event
view-if: consulation_day_trigger
max-visits: 1
on-arrival: {!
    // TODO: How does the preparation event affect this?
    // TODO: Roadmap updating if required?
    if (!Q.achievement_calcotada) {
        window.achievementNotif('Calçotada Popular', 'img/achievements/calcotada.png', 1);
    }
    this.achieve("calcotada");
    Q.consultation_happened = true;
    Q.consultation_pending = false;
!}

= Participative process of [+ month : month +] [+ year +]

Today, all Catalan residents 16 and over have been called to vote on the non-binding consulation on the political future of Catalonia. Participation is not easy to predict as, following the ruling of the Constitutional Court against the law allowing this consultation, PP[? if vox_parlament_s > 0: , Cs, and Vox?] [? if not vox_parlament_s > 0: and Cs ?]have announced a complete boicot of the consultation. [? if psc_leader == "Àngel Ros" or psc_leader == "Montserrat Tura": The PSC, while not thrilled by the idea of this consultation without an agreement, is at least somwhat supporting.?][? if not (psc_leader == "Àngel Ros" or psc_leader == "Montserrat Tura"): The PSC is not thrilled by the idea of this consultation without an agreement and has taken an ambivalent position, neither boicotting nor openly calling for participating in it, in yet another impossible balancing act.?] [? if icv_parlament_s > 0: ICV-EUiA?][? if csqp_parlament_s > 0: CSQP?][? if cecp_parlament_s > 0: CECP?][? if ecp_parlament_s > 0: ECP?] is calling their voters to make their voice heard[? if consultation_question = 2: , while officially supporting a vote for the Yes/No option?]. All pro-independence party naturally are enthusiastic about seeing the results.

- @direct
- @double
- @convoluted


@direct
title: Do you want Catalonia to become an independent state in the form of a republic?
view-if: consultation_question = 1
on-arrival: {!
    Q.consultation_yes = 0;
    Q.consultation_abst = 0;
    Q.consultation_no = 0;

    for (var constituency of Q.parlament_constituencies) {
        for (var demo of Q.parlament_demographics) {
            Q.consultation_yes += (Q["ciu_parlament_" + constituency + "_" + demo + "_support"] * 0.9 + Q["cdc_parlament_" + constituency + "_" + demo + "_support"] + Q["dl_parlament_" + constituency + "_" + demo + "_support"] + Q["pdcat_parlament_" + constituency + "_" + demo + "_support"] + Q["jxcat_parlament_" + constituency + "_" + demo + "_support"] + Q["junts_parlament_" + constituency + "_" + demo + "_support"] + Q["jxsi_parlament_" + constituency + "_" + demo + "_support"] + Q["erc_parlament_" + constituency + "_" + demo + "_support"] + Q["cup_parlament_" + constituency + "_" + demo + "_support"] + Q["fnc_parlament_" + constituency + "_" + demo + "_support"] + (Q["icv_parlament_" + constituency + "_" + demo + "_support"] + Q["csqp_parlament_" + constituency + "_" + demo + "_support"]) * 0.4 + Q["cecp_parlament_" + constituency + "_" + demo + "_support"] * 0.1) * Q["parlament_" + constituency + "_" + demo + "_pop"]/100;
            Q.consultation_no += (Q["ciu_parlament_" + constituency + "_" + demo + "_support"] * 0.1 + Q["unio_parlament_" + constituency + "_" + demo + "_support"] + (Q["icv_parlament_" + constituency + "_" + demo + "_support"] + Q["csqp_parlament_" + constituency + "_" + demo + "_support"]) * 0.4 + Q["cecp_parlament_" + constituency + "_" + demo + "_support"] * 0.6) * Q["parlament_" + constituency + "_" + demo + "_pop"]/100;
            Q.consultation_abst += ((Q["icv_parlament_" + constituency + "_" + demo + "_support"] + Q["csqp_parlament_" + constituency + "_" + demo + "_support"]) * 0.2 +  Q["cecp_parlament_" + constituency + "_" + demo + "_support"] * 0.3 +  Q["ppc_parlament_" + constituency + "_" + demo + "_support"] + Q["cs_parlament_" + constituency + "_" + demo + "_support"] + Q["vox_parlament_" + constituency + "_" + demo + "_support"] + Q["abstain_parlament_" + constituency + "_" + demo + "_support"]) * Q["parlament_" + constituency + "_" + demo + "_pop"]/100;
            switch (Q.psc_leader) {
                case "Àngel Ros":
                    Q.consultation_abst += (Q["psc_parlament_" + constituency + "_" + demo + "_support"] * 0.4)* Q["parlament_" + constituency + "_" + demo + "_pop"]/100;
                    Q.consultation_no += (Q["psc_parlament_" + constituency + "_" + demo + "_support"] * 0.4)* Q["parlament_" + constituency + "_" + demo + "_pop"]/100;
                    Q.consultation_yes += (Q["psc_parlament_" + constituency + "_" + demo + "_support"] * 0.2)* Q["parlament_" + constituency + "_" + demo + "_pop"]/100;
                    break;
                case "Montserrat Tura":
                    Q.consultation_abst += (Q["psc_parlament_" + constituency + "_" + demo + "_support"] * 0.3)* Q["parlament_" + constituency + "_" + demo + "_pop"]/100;
                    Q.consultation_no += (Q["psc_parlament_" + constituency + "_" + demo + "_support"] * 0.4)* Q["parlament_" + constituency + "_" + demo + "_pop"]/100;
                    Q.consultation_yes += (Q["psc_parlament_" + constituency + "_" + demo + "_support"] * 0.3)* Q["parlament_" + constituency + "_" + demo + "_pop"]/100;
                    break;
                default:
                    Q.consultation_abst += (Q["psc_parlament_" + constituency + "_" + demo + "_support"] * 0.85)* Q["parlament_" + constituency + "_" + demo + "_pop"]/100;
                    Q.consultation_no += (Q["psc_parlament_" + constituency + "_" + demo + "_support"] * 0.1)* Q["parlament_" + constituency + "_" + demo + "_pop"]/100;
                    Q.consultation_yes += (Q["psc_parlament_" + constituency + "_" + demo + "_support"] * 0.05)* Q["parlament_" + constituency + "_" + demo + "_pop"]/100;
                    break;
            }            
        }
    }
    Q.consultation_yes = Math.ceil(Q.consultation_yes);
    Q.consultation_abst = Math.ceil(Q.consultation_abst);
    Q.consultation_no = Math.ceil(Q.consultation_no);

    Q.consultation_total_votes = Q.consultation_no + Q.consultation_yes;
    Q.consultation_participation_pc = Math.round((Q.consultation_total_votes/ (Q.consultation_total_votes + Q.consultation_abst)) * 1000) / 10;
    Q.consultation_yes_pc = Math.round((Q.consultation_yes / Q.consultation_total_votes) * 1000) / 10;
    Q.consultation_no_pc = Math.round((Q.consultation_no / Q.consultation_total_votes) * 1000) / 10;

    // Add thousands notation
    Q.consultation_yes = Q.consultation_yes.toString().replace(/\B(?=(\d{3})+(?!\d))/g, '.');
    Q.consultation_no = Q.consultation_no.toString().replace(/\B(?=(\d{3})+(?!\d))/g, '.');
!}

**Do you want Catalonia to become an independent state in the form of a republic?**

{!<table style='border-spacing: 0px; margin-right: 1em; width:95%; table-layout: fixed;'>!}
{!<tr><td style='width: 4.5em'> YES </td><td style='height: 2em; background-color: #008000; border-radius: 0 3px 3px 0; color: white; text-align: center; width: !}[+ consultation_yes_pc +]{!%'>!}[?if consultation_yes_pc > 12 :[+ consultation_yes +] ?]{!</td><td style="padding-left:0.5em;">!}[?if consultation_yes_pc < 12 : <span style="font-size:0.9em">[+ consultation_yes +]</span> | ?][+ consultation_yes_pc +]{!%</td></tr>!}
{!</table>!}
{!<table style='border-spacing: 0px; margin-right: 1em; width:95%; table-layout: fixed;'>!}
{!<tr><td style='width: 4.5em'> NO </td><td style='height: 2em; background-color: #c30000; border-radius: 0 3px 3px 0; color: white; text-align: center; width: !}[+ consultation_no_pc +]{!%'>!}[?if consultation_no_pc > 12 :[+ consultation_no +]?]{!</td><td style="padding-left:0.5em;">!}[?if consultation_no_pc < 12 : <span style="font-size:0.9em">[+ consultation_no +]</span> | ?] [+ consultation_no_pc +]{!%</td></tr>!}
{!</table>!}
{!<div style="width: 95%;text-align: center; margin-top:-0.75em;">!} **Turnout:**  [+ consultation_participation_pc +]% {!</div>!}
{!<div style="width: 95%; justify-content: center; display:flex;"><div class="box" style="width: 70%; border-radius: 3px; background-color: #ccc"><div class="box" style=" height: 1em; background-color: dimgrey; margin-right: 0.5em; border-radius: 3px; width:!}[+ consultation_participation_pc +]{!%;"></div></div></div>!}

- @after
